         AAAtAQAABQAAABQC6QJIAAUAAAATAvcESAAFAAAAFALpAs4BBQAAABMC8AMvAgUAAAAUAvAD
         LwIFAAAAEwL3BM4BEAAAAPsCQP4AAAAAAACQAQAAAAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAALQEBAAgA
         AAAyClwGugYBAAAA9wAIAAAAMgquBLoGAQAAAPcACAAAADIK/gK6BgEAAAD3AAgAAAAyCnsH
         ugYBAAAA+AAIAAAAMgrfAboGAQAAAPYACAAAADIKXAbxAwEAAADnAAgAAAAyCq4E8QMBAAAA
         5wAIAAAAMgr+AvEDAQAAAOcACAAAADIKewfxAwEAAADoAAgAAAAyCt8B8QMBAAAA5gAIAAAA
         MgpgBKgCAQAAAD0AFQAAAPsCIP8AAAAAAACQAQEAAAAEAgAQVGltZXMgTmV3IFJvbWFuAAB+
         BAAAAC0BAgAEAAAA8AEBAAgAAAAyCnAH6QUBAAAAbgAQAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAQAAAgQC
         ABBTeW1ib2wAAgQAAAAtAQEABAAAAPABAgAIAAAAMgoAB6cEAQAAAGEACAAAADIKuQGnBAEA
         AABhAAgAAAAyCmAEbwABAAAAYQARAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAAAAAgQCABBNVCBFeHRyYQAC
         BAAAAC0BAgAEAAAA8AEBAAgAAAAyCmAEFwUBAAAATQAVAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAAAAAAQC
         ABBUaW1lcyBOZXcgUm9tYW4AAH4EAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQIACAAAADIKYATYBAEAAAAgABUA
         AAD7AiD/AAAAAAAAkAEAAAAABAIAEFRpbWVzIE5ldyBSb21hbgAAfgQAAAAtAQIABAAAAPAB
         AQAIAAAAMgopAtAFAQAAADEACgAAACYGDwAKAP////8BAAAAAAAQAAAA+wIUAAkAAAAAALwC
         AAAAAAECAiJTeXN0ZW0AAAQAAAAtAQEABAAAAPABAgADAAAAAAA=
        </office:binary-data>
       </draw:image>
      </draw:frame>. Ogni numero complesso è associato ad uno dei possibili valori che può assumere la grandezza <text:span text:style-name="T1">g</text:span>, <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object12" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.8673in" svg:height="0.222in" draw:z-index="6"><draw:object>
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
