         AAAmBg8ACgD/////AQAAAAAAEAAAAPsCFAAJAAAAAAC8AgAAAAABAgIiU3lzdGVtAAAEAAAA
         LQEBAAQAAADwAQIAAwAAAAAA
        </office:binary-data>
       </draw:image>
      </draw:frame>Il modulo quadrato di ognuno di questi numeri complessi, ad esempio <text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">k</text:span>, da la probabilità che misurando la grandezza <text:span text:style-name="T1">g</text:span> esca il particolare valore <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object13" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.1736in" svg:height="0.222in" draw:z-index="7"><draw:object>
