       BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADALAAQAEEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
       9////8ADAAC3AQAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAAAwAAkAAAD6AgAAEAAAAAAAAAAiAAQA
       AAAtAQAABQAAABQCVQD3AgUAAAATAlUAuwMVAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAQAAAAQCABBUaW1l
       cyBOZXcgUm9tYW4AAH4EAAAALQEBAAgAAAAyCmAB6QIBAAAAeAAIAAAAMgpgAU4AAQAAAHgA
       EAAAAPsCQP4AAAAAAACQAQAAAAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAALQECAAQAAADwAQEACAAAADIK
       YAF8AQEAAAA9AAoAAAAmBg8ACgD/////AQAAAAAAEAAAAPsCFAAJAAAAAAC8AgAAAAABAgIi
       U3lzdGVtAAAEAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQIAAwAAAAAA
      </office:binary-data>
     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame>, quindi quando si esegue una misura di <text:span text:style-name="T1">x</text:span> si otterrà per forza il valore <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object28" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.1098in" svg:height="0.1854in" draw:z-index="22"><draw:object>
