   <text:p text:style-name="Standard"><text:soft-page-break/>No, perché il simbolo <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object61" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.2335in" svg:height="0.1945in" draw:z-index="55"><draw:object>
