         AQAAAAAAEAAAAPsCFAAJAAAAAAC8AgAAAAABAgIiU3lzdGVtAAAEAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQIA
         AwAAAAAA
        </office:binary-data>
       </draw:image>
      </draw:frame>. Ogni numero complesso è associato ad una delle possibili combinazione di valori che può assumere la n-upla di grandezze <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object74" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.5047in" svg:height="0.222in" draw:z-index="68"><draw:object>
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
         <semantics>
          <mrow>
           <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
            <mrow>
             <msub>
              <mi>g</mi>
              <mstyle mathsize="8pt">
               <mn>1</mn>
              </mstyle>
             </msub>
             <mo stretchy="false">…</mo>
             <msub>
              <mi>g</mi>
              <mstyle mathsize="8pt">
               <mi>n</mi>
              </mstyle>
             </msub>
            </mrow>
           </mstyle>
           <mrow/>
          </mrow>
          <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{g rSub { size 8{1} }  dotslow g rSub { size 8{n} } } {}</annotation>
         </semantics>
        </math>
       </draw:object><draw:image>
        <office:binary-data>AQAJAAADAAEAAAIAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
