       </draw:image>
      </draw:frame><text:s/>e che il sistema si porti nell’autostato simultaneo <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object78" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="2.1126in" svg:height="0.2575in" draw:z-index="72"><draw:object>
