    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P7">In generale se il sistema si trova in uno stato <text:span text:style-name="T2"></text:span> e si misura contemporaneamente un set completo di grandezze <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object79" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.5047in" svg:height="0.2457in" draw:z-index="73"><draw:object>
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
         <semantics>
          <mrow>
           <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
            <mrow>
             <msubsup>
              <mi>g</mi>
              <mstyle mathsize="8pt">
               <mn>1</mn>
              </mstyle>
              <mi>&apos;</mi>
             </msubsup>
             <mo stretchy="false">…</mo>
             <msubsup>
              <mi>g</mi>
              <mstyle mathsize="8pt">
               <mi>n</mi>
              </mstyle>
              <mi>&apos;</mi>
             </msubsup>
            </mrow>
           </mstyle>
           <mrow/>
          </mrow>
          <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ { {g}} sup { &apos; } rSub { size 8{1} }  dotslow  { {g}} sup { &apos; } rSub { size 8{n} } } {}</annotation>
         </semantics>
        </math>
       </draw:object><draw:image>
        <office:binary-data>AQAJAAADKAEAAAIAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
