       AAAAAA==
      </office:binary-data>
     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame>. (D’ora in avanti con i simboli sopralineati indicheremo le grandezze vettoriali).</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2">Ampiezze di probabilità per la quantità di moto.</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Se conosciamo lo stato di una particella materiale, e conosciamo la distribuzione di ampiezze di probabilità per la variabile posizione <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object106" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.6862in" svg:height="0.2055in" draw:z-index="100"><draw:object>
      <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
       <semantics>
        <mrow>
         <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
          <mrow>
           <mi>ψ</mi>
           <mrow>
            <mo fence="true" form="prefix" stretchy="true">(</mo>
            <mrow>
             <mrow>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mi>,</mi>
              <mi>y</mi>
              <mi>,</mi>
              <mi>z</mi>
             </mrow>
            </mrow>
            <mo fence="true" form="postfix" stretchy="true">)</mo>
           </mrow>
          </mrow>
         </mstyle>
         <mrow/>
        </mrow>
        <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ψ left (x,y,z right )} {}</annotation>
       </semantics>
      </math>
     </draw:object><draw:image>
      <office:binary-data>AQAJAAADKgEAAAIAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
       BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADAJgAqAGEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
       t////2AGAAAXAgAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAABgABAAAAD7Arz9CQEAAAAAkAEAAAAC
       BAIAEFN5bWJvbAACBAAAAC0BAAAIAAAAMgqeAXIBAQAAACgAEAAAAPsCvP0JAQAAAACQAQAA
       AAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQAACAAAADIKngEABgEAAAApABUAAAD7AkD+
       AAAAAAAAkAEBAAAABAIAEFRpbWVzIE5ldyBSb21hbgAAgwQAAAAtAQAABAAAAPABAQAIAAAA
       MgqgASkFAQAAAHoACAAAADIKoAGmAwEAAAB5AAgAAAAyCqABFQIBAAAAeAAVAAAA+wJA/gAA
       AAAAAJABAAAAAAQCABBUaW1lcyBOZXcgUm9tYW4AAIMEAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQAACAAAADIK
       oAF4BAEAAAAsAAgAAAAyCqAB4AIBAAAALAAQAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAQAAAgQCABBTeW1i
       b2wAAgQAAAAtAQAABAAAAPABAQAIAAAAMgqgAfr/AQAAAHkACgAAACYGDwAKAP////8BAAAA
