    </draw:frame><text:s/>“contiene in se” gli autostati che stiamo cercando <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object121" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.5181in" svg:height="0.2457in" draw:z-index="121"><draw:object>
