      </draw:frame><text:s/>nei quali si ottiene con certezza il valore <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object156" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.1417in" svg:height="0.2091in" draw:z-index="156"><draw:object>
