    </draw:frame><text:s/>un autoket rappresentativo di un autostato simultaneo delle grandezze <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object204" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.1098in" svg:height="0.1854in" draw:z-index="204"><draw:object>
