   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2">L’energia.</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Come ultima grandezza di studio consideriamo l’energia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Nel formalismo della Meccanica Classica, per una particella carica in un potenziale elettrico, abbiamo l’energia</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard"><text:tab/><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object219" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="1.0575in" svg:height="0.3953in" draw:z-index="219"><draw:object>
